{"tid":1281002,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"金鐘夏日潑水節開始啦","createTime":"2019-07-03T07:01:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T11:44:21.000Z","uid":169865,"like":690,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"aa3aa6246ab4b7fe20188aaddbf18ee5e7c52d12","tid":1281002,"uid":169865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:01:15.000Z","msg":"大家都知泰國不嬲都有潑水節<br />\n泰國人都有係香港攪過潑水節，深受港人歡迎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港作為咁焗咁熱既城市點可以錯過咁正既消暑活動<br />\n<br />\n傳統泰國人係將水放落啲容器度，例如汽球、膠袋，水槍到射去對方到消暑<br />\n反觀睇下近日香港人係金鐘有咩方法消暑呢？<br />\n傘，舉傘之後都係舉傘<br />\n又焗又重，一打開傘周圍啲人又開，上一把下一把，到底要曬幾多力先舉得起把遮？<br />\n舉完我仲熱過唔舉，仲辛苦又冇力應付之後既夏日活動<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">重點：開完遮睇唔到前面，有邊個行緊埋黎想知都有一定困難<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n所以小弟覺得香港人好應該攪返個屬於香港既潑水節<br />\n唔好攪到自己咁辛苦，中暑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">舉辦地點：金鐘一帶</span></span><br />\n<br />\n當然必要時都係要<span style=\"color: red;\">返把遮擋一擋對家啲潑水攻勢</span><br />\n再黎波遠攻還擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過緊記<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">千祈唔好入墨水，臭蛋液落去容器到玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好入墨水，臭蛋液落去容器到玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好入墨水，臭蛋液落去容器到玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n射到，整烏糟人地就唔好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你知道<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">整黑人地副眼鏡眼罩 睇唔到野</span></span>好麻煩架麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">整臭人地</span></span>心情又唔好，士氣差<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n約定大家啊，金鐘夏日潑水節<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有咩細節大家再傾<br />\n不過記得係免費入場<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">到時可能會有警方人士維持活動，大家記得幫佢地消暑</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HRFfx14.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHRFfx14.png&h=8979d52a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Btw 都係個句千祈唔好入墨水，臭蛋液落去容器到玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"502939cfb439a1e66b054b2d69fa2efde58d8fcb","tid":1281002,"uid":169865,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:02:08.000Z","msg":"自推一波10連"},{"pid":"ef7f4e76749d7fbd3a0c2ab0e4602f19b101f9b0","tid":1281002,"uid":169865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:02:18.000Z","msg":"1推"},{"pid":"c6f88d79cfc159e2d58103fe511e77daf127a1a8","tid":1281002,"uid":169865,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:02:28.000Z","msg":"2推"},{"pid":"b2d801fd9488d5b76fd0eef25c611f5825f05099","tid":1281002,"uid":169865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:02:38.000Z","msg":"3推"},{"pid":"0ac502d2bdb0226418cecda9db653eca74c968b9","tid":1281002,"uid":169865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:02:49.000Z","msg":"4推"},{"pid":"70750705069068e88fdb8c2eb81f606ced270a18","tid":1281002,"uid":169865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T07:02:59.000Z","msg":"5推"},{"pid":"9a66cf26351ea9b868a89fb74e1546655e612d43","tid":1281002,"uid":169865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"